    "Mann served as a senior tech leader at Wix.com, an Israeli provider of cloud-based web development tools, from 2010 to 2012. Wix IPO'd in 2013.",
    "A serial entrepreneur, Mann cofounded two other companies before joining Wix: Facebook app Save An Alien and digital marketing firm ntt.co.il."
